summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 through 6, Block 39, Moss' 1st Addition to South Seattle, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-388 and 17-293, respectively.
note: Near what is now the I-5 and West Seattle Freeway Interchange.
